getting the present universe.

00:56:32.510 --> 00:56:36.710
--there'd be a further
coasting expansion

00:56:36.710 --> 00:56:39.140
from the end of
inflation until now,

00:56:39.140 --> 00:56:43.740
which can just be calculated
by using the idea that a times

00:56:43.740 --> 00:56:47.130
